infra.name: te0803_3eg_1e
infra.description: Zynq UltraScale+ TE0803-*-3BE31-A (8GB DDR) Board (form factor 5.2x7.6 cm) with 4x 2 GByte DDR4, speed grade -1 and extended temperature range. *Supported PCB Revisions: REV03. Board Part is only with minimum PS-Setup. Use for own carrier or simple SDK debugging. User must configure B2B MIOs manually, depending on his carrier board connection. Without user PS configuration only JTAG and QSPI boot is possible with this board part file.
infra.author: trenz.biz
